#. Plugin Name of the plugin
msgid "Popups Nekuda"
msgstr "פופאפים נקודה"

#: popup.php:120
msgid "Popups"
msgstr "פופאפים"

#: popup.php:121
msgid "Popup"
msgstr "פופאפ"

#: popup.php:122
msgid "Add New"
